{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key0908|text', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|EpistleProkeimenon|text', 'text' : 'Truly blessed is the way that you travel on today; for a place has been prepared for your everlasting rest.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|brightweek|R091', 'text' : 'Then the Epistle and Gospel readings for the day.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1101|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 2.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1101|melody', 'text' : 'Joseph took You down.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1101|text', 'text' : 'Brethren, let us give a final kiss * of farewell to him/her who is dead now, and offer thanks to God. * For he/she has departed from his/her friends and family. * He/she is ready for burial, no longer concerned with * anything of vanity or of the weary flesh. * Where now are the friends and the family? * Therefore let us pray to the Lord God, * that He will give rest to him/her who parts from us.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1102|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 2.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1102|melody', 'text' : 'Joseph took You down.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1102|text', 'text' : 'Brethren, separation is so hard. * Such a lamentation, such grieving, at this grave turn of events. * Come to kiss him/her who was with us just a short time ago. * He/she is taken for burial, and lies six feet under, * dwelling in the darkness now, buried alongside the dead. * Come, now, all his/ her friends and his/her family. * Fervently we pray to the Lord God, * that He will give rest to him/her who parts from us.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1103|mode', 'text' : 'Mode 2.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1103|melody', 'text' : 'Joseph took You down.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1103|text', 'text' : 'Save those who have placed their hope in you, * Mother of the Sun never-setting, and Theotokos all-pure. * We entreat you pray to God the most benevolent, * that He grant everlasting rest, * by your intercessions, * to the one departed, where the souls of righteous repose. * Grant that he/she inherit the good things * that our God prepared, in the dwellings * of the righteous, for eternal memory.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1104|mode', 'text' : 'Mode pl. 2.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1104|melody', 'text' : 'Idiomelon.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1104|text', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1105|mode', 'text' : 'Mode pl. 2.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1105|melody', 'text' : 'O Christ, as it is written.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1105|text', 'text' : 'O Christ, at the entreaties of her * who bore You, and of all the Saints, * of your Martyrs, * your Apostles, Hierarchs, * monastic Saints and Prophets, * together with the Righteous, * repose Your servants who have fallen asleep.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|brightweek|R111', 'text' : 'Instead of the final hymns, "Brethren, let us give a final kiss," etc. we sing the following:'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|brightweek|R112', 'text' : 'On exiting the church, the following is sung, instead of Holy God:'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1200|title', 'text' : 'THE BURIAL'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1300|title', 'text' : 'For Clergy.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1301|text', 'text' : 'You who proclaimed the Gospel of the Lamb of God * and who were yourselves like lambs slaughtered, * and were translated to life that is immortal and eternal, * earnestly entreat Him, O holy martyr Saints, * that He grant us remission of all our debts.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1302|text', 'text' : 'All you who during your earthly life * walked the narrow way full of hardships, * who taking up the cross as a yoke * followed after Me believing, * come now and enjoy the rewards * and the heavenly crowns that I prepared for you.'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1303|title', 'text' : 'Prayer for a Deceased Priest'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1303|text', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1400|title', 'text' : 'Dismissal'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1401|text', 'text' : 'He who as immortal King has authority over the living and the dead and who rose from the dead,'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1402|text', 'text' : 'through the intercessions of his most pure and holy Mother,'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1403|text', 'text' : 'the holy, glorious, and praise­worthy Apostles,'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1404|text', 'text' : 'our holy and God-bearing Fathers,'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1405|text', 'text' : 'of the holy and glorious forefathers Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob;'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1406|text', 'text' : 'of His holy and righteous friend Lazarus, who lay in the grave four days;'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1407|text', 'text' : 'and all the saints,'}
{'id_' : 'eu|funeral_en_US_dedes|euFUN|Key1408|text', 'text' : 'establish the soul of His servant (Name), departed from us, in the dwelling place of the saints; give rest to him (her) in the bosom of Abraham; and number him (her) among the righteous.'}
